Ei, Sheldon!

121
00:05:57,672 --> 00:06:01,184
Olá, Billy Sparks.
Olá, Matilda Sparks.

122
00:06:01,233 --> 00:06:03,416
Ouvi dizer que vai
ao colégio amanhã.

123
00:06:03,442 --> 00:06:05,920
